	(540,'Build Your Own Web Framework In Go','https://www.nicolasmerouze.com/build-web-framework-golang/','Build Your Own Web Framework In Go\r\nWhen Martini was released, it quickly became the most popular Go web framework and it still is. But it is not idiomatic, it is slow and the concept is flawed, the author said it himself. It taught bad practices to a lot of new Go developers. Despite these facts, lots of developers are using it because it is very easy to get started with it and it\'s a very good reason!\r\n','2019-12-03 00:18:01',71),
