	(592,'Object-Oriented PHP for Beginners','https://code.tutsplus.com/tutorials/object-oriented-php-for-beginners--net-12762?__cf_chl_captcha_tk__=2412ed7a0485e27c55480dbdeeaf73df95e468f4-1582328136-0-AU8C6IPq3Mpo5CDyJI1vKMkIbk0OwO1NrBFHWyXgcM1iRVA-4-GuCLubjhK6mfGVTFpjHi252E26yAwffBY5-AA5BQqkkpPZfw0ywJ3d2qMWlu20FZDwFu0iWhUoqdOT6pfxyv6ktsIIIkF_rpo5DyrgRy597XmbvwU6H9wuiph5XaqqkqLWW9W1FAEFgZ992DIxj4F8NhBHAIdgbv23bzWhAHmA2oCKH3kBFnP7idTqtNS-zGl9Ahw0M1o6H7T-8L_G0ceNj6grADBG_GvZDjmbOgMGFSpC0aLOljI3rrX6rsoltf6W4x2A39rz6kQPKW_kvUUkFqyEns6Xqmr7hifgZJCDQ-AoOQPhvzVRhmZGo7eo4iyVg6RISnoq1G0ln-TrvOYwOvTuhPCM23ZmJms','For many PHP programmers, object-oriented programming is a frightening concept, full of complicated syntax and other roadblocks. As detailed in my book, Pro PHP and jQuery, you\'ll learn the concepts behind object-oriented programming (OOP), a style of coding in which related actions are grouped into classes to aid in creating more-compact, effective code.\r\n\r\nTo see what you can do with object-oriented PHP, take a look at the huge range of PHP scripts on CodeCanyon, such as this SQLite Object-Oriented Framework.\r\n\r\nOr, if you\'re struggling with the do-it-yourself approach, you could hire a professional on Envato Studio either to fix errors for you or to create full PHP applications and modules.','2020-02-22 10:39:04',19),
	(593,'除了 SSR，就没有别的办法了吗？','https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/57375824','没有什么是 jQuery 一把梭搞不定的\r\n一般接到这类“简单”的需求，相信绝大部分人的第一反应肯定是 jQuery，尽管它早已落入前端鄙视链的最底层，但依然魅力不减，宝刀未老。配合 BootStrap 又是一把梭，分分钟搞定。\r\n\r\n时至今日，这套方案依然可行，很好的满足了业务的需求，对开发者的技术要求也不高，可以说是非常稳了。\r\n\r\n那不就行了，你还担心啥？','2020-02-23 16:14:14',3),
